WEBVTT

00:00:19.162 --> 00:00:24.349
♪The whole world is lit up♪

00:00:24.350 --> 00:00:25.661
♪Because you exist♪

00:00:25.662 --> 00:00:27.741
♪You're always♪

00:00:27.742 --> 00:00:32.391
♪Somewhere close, flying with me♪

00:00:32.392 --> 00:00:35.124
♪Go to where the wind blows♪

00:00:35.125 --> 00:00:36.691
♪Hold tight♪

00:00:36.692 --> 00:00:42.481
♪To the ray of light that belongs to us♪

00:00:42.482 --> 00:00:47.920
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 10=

00:00:50.820 --> 00:00:51.938
I can prove it.

00:00:51.939 --> 00:00:54.978
Ms. Mu would never secretly
swap the painting.

00:00:54.979 --> 00:00:57.460
Who are you?
What gives you the right to prove that?

00:00:57.540 --> 00:00:59.258
Isn't she Assistant Yan
from Hong Studio?

00:00:59.259 --> 00:01:00.540
She was on the news before.

00:01:01.019 --> 00:01:03.978
Earlier, Ms. Mu already returned the restored
"Classic of Mountains and Seas"

00:01:03.979 --> 00:01:05.220
to the studio.

00:01:05.300 --> 00:01:06.980
It'll be exhibited to the public
very soon.

00:01:07.540 --> 00:01:08.739
Today, I'm here

00:01:08.740 --> 00:01:09.978
on behalf of Mr. Hong

00:01:09.979 --> 00:01:11.980
to discuss a potential collaboration
with Ms. Mu.

00:01:12.900 --> 00:01:14.659
If you don't have any questions,

00:01:14.660 --> 00:01:16.019
you may leave now.

00:01:16.020 --> 00:01:16.900
By the way,

00:01:17.180 --> 00:01:18.780
make sure you report the facts.

00:01:18.900 --> 00:01:20.138
Otherwise, Hong Studio

00:01:20.139 --> 00:01:21.780
will hold you accountable.

00:01:22.180 --> 00:01:22.858
Really?

00:01:22.859 --> 00:01:24.099
Has Hong Studio decided

00:01:24.100 --> 00:01:25.899
to collaborate with Mu Group?

00:01:25.900 --> 00:01:26.539
Ms. Mu,

00:01:26.540 --> 00:01:28.420
could you tell us a bit
about the collaboration?

00:01:31.979 --> 00:01:33.099
About what happened earlier,

00:01:33.100 --> 00:01:34.819
thank you for stepping in, Miss Yan.

00:01:35.139 --> 00:01:36.049
You're welcome.

00:01:36.050 --> 00:01:38.329
I only came
because Mr. Hong asked me to.

00:01:38.740 --> 00:01:40.939
Ms. Mu, you sure have
quite the influence.

00:01:42.300 --> 00:01:43.459
(What's Boss up to)

00:01:43.460 --> 00:01:45.179
(this time?)

00:01:46.300 --> 00:01:47.618
Mr. Hong

00:01:47.619 --> 00:01:49.179
has read your proposal.

00:01:49.259 --> 00:01:51.379
He's marked the parts he'd like revised.

00:01:51.380 --> 00:01:53.060
The rest is up to you now, Ms. Mu.

00:01:54.499 --> 00:01:55.459
I should get going then.

00:01:55.460 --> 00:01:56.579
Let's keep in touch.

00:02:03.779 --> 00:02:05.659
Mr. Hong

00:02:05.779 --> 00:02:07.340
is really something.

00:02:08.619 --> 00:02:10.218
How did he calculate it so perfectly

00:02:10.219 --> 00:02:12.259
that Miss Yan would show up
at just the right time

00:02:12.260 --> 00:02:14.220
to talk to me about collaboration?

00:02:18.099 --> 00:02:20.419
I used to think he had
too much personality

00:02:20.700 --> 00:02:22.740
and might be difficult to work with.

00:02:23.860 --> 00:02:24.939
But now it seems

00:02:25.580 --> 00:02:28.460
that although he looks cold
on the outside,

00:02:28.980 --> 00:02:29.899
he's actually

00:02:29.900 --> 00:02:31.259
quite helpful.

00:02:32.819 --> 00:02:34.139
The appraisal report earlier

00:02:34.140 --> 00:02:35.939
seemed to be his help as well.

00:02:37.339 --> 00:02:39.460
I should find time to visit him.

00:02:47.059 --> 00:02:49.979
I was putting on an act
in front of Xu Mingzhu for you too.

00:02:50.300 --> 00:02:52.780
I stayed up for nights
watching Zhao Ye on the monitor

00:02:52.939 --> 00:02:54.859
to copy that footage while he was away.

00:02:54.860 --> 00:02:56.300
How is that the same?

00:02:56.499 --> 00:02:57.538
You and I

00:02:57.539 --> 00:02:59.220
are partners
in a mutually beneficial deal.

00:02:59.900 --> 00:03:01.419
But Mr. Hong

00:03:01.580 --> 00:03:04.259
helped without holding any grudges.

00:03:07.980 --> 00:03:09.379
It's only right for me to thank him.

00:03:11.300 --> 00:03:12.340
Figures.

00:03:12.779 --> 00:03:14.740
Women always like the new
and forget the old.

00:03:15.219 --> 00:03:17.419
They prefer new partners as well.

00:03:21.900 --> 00:03:24.659
Why do I smell so much jealousy,
Captain Shen?

00:03:25.339 --> 00:03:26.900
It's just cooperation.

00:03:27.020 --> 00:03:28.939
Is there really a need for that sarcasm?

00:03:31.460 --> 00:03:32.740
Or

00:03:33.619 --> 00:03:35.580
do you have some feelings for me?

00:03:42.339 --> 00:03:44.379
You're overthinking it, Ms. Mu.

00:03:46.860 --> 00:03:48.620
We're only partners.

00:03:49.740 --> 00:03:51.179
I just wanted to remind you

00:03:51.180 --> 00:03:53.379
who your real partner is.

00:03:55.059 --> 00:03:55.498
Alright.

00:03:55.499 --> 00:03:57.419
This incident actually gave me a new idea.

00:03:57.420 --> 00:03:58.740
I'd like to discuss with you.

00:04:01.779 --> 00:04:03.939
I will not allow something like this
to happen again.

00:04:07.140 --> 00:04:07.979
Also,

00:04:08.499 --> 00:04:10.739
go deal with
the forged seal issue immediately.

00:04:10.740 --> 00:04:12.579
Now that Hong reaches out to Mu Zhiyu,

00:04:12.580 --> 00:04:14.859
if this matter gets exposed,
I won't be able to protect you.

00:04:20.979 --> 00:04:21.859
Come in.

00:04:22.859 --> 00:04:23.940
Ms. Xu,

00:04:24.219 --> 00:04:26.859
I didn't expect the dashcam footage
to be recovered.

00:04:26.900 --> 00:04:28.940
I won't allow something like this
to happen again.

00:04:29.060 --> 00:04:29.858
Ms. Xu,

00:04:29.859 --> 00:04:31.700
I suspect the car may have been bugged.

00:04:31.900 --> 00:04:33.419
It needs a full inspection.

00:04:40.260 --> 00:04:41.260
Go ahead.

00:05:00.020 --> 00:05:00.700
Here.

00:05:01.260 --> 00:05:01.979
Over here.

00:05:07.179 --> 00:05:08.819
What took you so long
to steal a car key?

00:05:08.820 --> 00:05:10.020
Didn't I tell you to hurry?

00:05:10.099 --> 00:05:11.659
Relax. No one's here.

00:05:14.900 --> 00:05:16.340
Shen Jibai, you're insane.

00:05:16.460 --> 00:05:18.099
Trying to make someone see you?

00:05:20.500 --> 00:05:21.499
Shen Jibai,

00:05:21.779 --> 00:05:23.418
are you sure we can find my dad

00:05:23.419 --> 00:05:24.619
through the dashcam?

00:05:28.820 --> 00:05:31.419
When we were checking
the dashcam earlier, I noticed something.

00:05:31.620 --> 00:05:33.200
They're all the same type
of memory card.

00:05:33.200 --> 00:05:35.099
They record driving routes
from the past seven days.

00:05:35.460 --> 00:05:36.819
Within the last seven days,

00:05:36.820 --> 00:05:38.939
Xu Mingzhu skipped work only once

00:05:38.940 --> 00:05:40.499
and went somewhere else alone.

00:05:40.500 --> 00:05:41.739
She went to see my dad?

00:05:45.419 --> 00:05:47.178
If we check the driving route
for that day,

00:05:47.179 --> 00:05:48.260
we'll find it...

00:05:48.460 --> 00:05:49.299
What's wrong?

00:05:50.179 --> 00:05:51.019
Zhao Ye.

00:05:51.020 --> 00:05:51.979
Shen Jibai.

00:05:52.060 --> 00:05:52.820
Shen Jibai.

00:05:53.339 --> 00:05:54.539
What are you standing there for?

00:06:06.779 --> 00:06:07.900
Shen Jibai.

00:06:11.140 --> 00:06:12.220
Shen Jibai.

00:06:14.779 --> 00:06:16.020
Shen Jibai.

00:06:21.179 --> 00:06:21.978
What's wrong?

00:06:21.979 --> 00:06:23.778
I've been calling you.

00:06:23.779 --> 00:06:25.499
You really think this is your own car?

00:06:26.299 --> 00:06:27.579
I couldn't find the key just now.

00:06:27.580 --> 00:06:29.059
I was looking for it in the back seat.

00:06:29.060 --> 00:06:30.659
You can't even keep the car key well?

00:06:31.219 --> 00:06:33.418
I'm really curious about
what Ms. Xu sees in you.

00:06:33.419 --> 00:06:34.218
Someone like you

00:06:34.219 --> 00:06:36.059
is only good for running errands.

00:06:36.460 --> 00:06:37.619
Alright. Stop talking.

00:06:37.620 --> 00:06:38.480
Open the trunk.

00:06:38.480 --> 00:06:40.259
I need to fetch something important
for Ms. Xu.

00:06:40.260 --> 00:06:42.539
No time should be wasted.
You can't afford the consequences.

00:06:56.979 --> 00:06:58.659
Who are you trying to impress?

00:07:00.460 --> 00:07:01.179
Alright.

00:07:01.339 --> 00:07:02.499
Hurry up and check the car.

00:07:07.700 --> 00:07:08.940
Check the car?

00:07:09.820 --> 00:07:11.819
So Xu Mingzhu actually gave you the key.

00:07:11.820 --> 00:07:12.940
You didn't steal it at all.

00:07:13.779 --> 00:07:15.059
You were playing me?

00:07:15.419 --> 00:07:17.460
If I didn't pretend I stole it,

00:07:17.620 --> 00:07:18.858
how could I cooperate with you

00:07:18.859 --> 00:07:20.259
and act like a guilty thief?

00:07:20.260 --> 00:07:21.859
Shen Jibai, you...

00:07:41.260 --> 00:07:42.940
Let's get out first.

00:07:48.620 --> 00:07:51.059
Based on Xu Mingzhu's dashcam footage,

00:07:51.060 --> 00:07:53.140
we've located the hospital
where Chairman Mu is staying.

00:07:53.620 --> 00:07:54.419
That's great.

00:07:54.580 --> 00:07:55.619
I finally found my dad.

00:07:55.620 --> 00:07:57.582
(Inpatient Department)

00:08:10.137 --> 00:08:11.097
(Dad,)

00:08:11.099 --> 00:08:12.739
(I came too late.)

00:08:13.020 --> 00:08:14.380
(You've suffered so much.)

00:08:17.659 --> 00:08:19.859
(I never expected the Mu Chenzhou
I searched so hard for)

00:08:19.900 --> 00:08:21.619
(to be in this state.)

00:08:21.900 --> 00:08:23.859
(The transfer records among
my mom's belongings)

00:08:24.179 --> 00:08:26.059
(were all signed by Mu Group.)

00:08:26.659 --> 00:08:28.340
(Were those transfers made by you?)

00:08:29.099 --> 00:08:30.260
(If it was,)

00:08:31.060 --> 00:08:33.060
(what's your relationship
with my family?)

00:08:33.740 --> 00:08:35.019
(And if it wasn't,)

00:08:36.062 --> 00:08:38.102
(then who made the transfers?)

00:08:39.179 --> 00:08:40.540
(No matter what,)

00:08:40.779 --> 00:08:42.859
(I'll get to the bottom of it.)

00:08:44.980 --> 00:08:45.899
Doctor,

00:08:45.939 --> 00:08:47.340
how's my dad's condition?

00:08:47.500 --> 00:08:48.899
Can he be discharged?

00:08:49.220 --> 00:08:49.979
I want to

00:08:49.980 --> 00:08:51.058
take him home.

00:08:51.059 --> 00:08:52.420
What's going on

00:08:52.500 --> 00:08:53.979
with your family?

00:08:54.340 --> 00:08:57.180
He's only been hospitalized for a few days,
and now you want him discharged?

00:08:57.340 --> 00:08:58.019
Seriously?

00:08:58.140 --> 00:08:59.778
Are you trying to exhaust him?

00:08:59.779 --> 00:09:00.538
Doctor,

00:09:00.539 --> 00:09:01.698
I'm his daughter.

00:09:01.699 --> 00:09:03.460
I can make this decision.

00:09:04.419 --> 00:09:05.538
If he stays in the hospital,

00:09:05.539 --> 00:09:06.859
he'll only be in more danger.

00:09:06.980 --> 00:09:08.379
I have to take him away immediately.

00:09:09.100 --> 00:09:11.058
I'll arrange the best medical team

00:09:11.059 --> 00:09:12.460
and equipment for him.

00:09:18.740 --> 00:09:19.779
Alright then.

00:09:20.059 --> 00:09:21.298
If you can provide

00:09:21.299 --> 00:09:23.379
the best medical team and equipment
at home,

00:09:23.459 --> 00:09:24.660
then going home

00:09:24.740 --> 00:09:26.019
is possible.

00:09:26.100 --> 00:09:27.940
What the patient must avoid right now

00:09:28.299 --> 00:09:29.820
is moving around.

00:09:30.459 --> 00:09:33.460
Staying at home for a long period
would actually be good for him.

00:09:34.100 --> 00:09:34.940
Well.

00:09:35.179 --> 00:09:35.818
Come with me.

00:09:35.819 --> 00:09:37.660
Let's settle the discharge fee.

00:09:37.740 --> 00:09:39.220
I don't think he should be discharged.

00:09:49.337 --> 00:09:53.567
♪Light comes beaming in♪

00:09:53.707 --> 00:09:58.076
♪Landing on my skin♪

00:09:58.077 --> 00:10:02.567
♪Warms the space you left behind♪

00:10:06.787 --> 00:10:10.726
♪Shadows move around♪

00:10:10.727 --> 00:10:15.336
♪Awake, racing thoughts♪

00:10:15.337 --> 00:10:19.867
♪Try to keep the memories safe♪

00:10:23.467 --> 00:10:29.257
♪Don't slip away♪

00:10:31.707 --> 00:10:36.276
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:36.277 --> 00:10:40.676
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:40.677 --> 00:10:44.997
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:45.017 --> 00:10:48.997
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:49.467 --> 00:10:53.776
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:53.777 --> 00:10:58.106
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:58.107 --> 00:11:02.416
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:02.417 --> 00:11:08.567
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪